20
00:02:04,820 --> 00:02:07,128
You... You have betrayed Her Lordship.

21
00:02:07,128 --> 00:02:09,947
And the Yu Clan. Why have you come here?

22
00:02:09,947 --> 00:02:14,127
Do you intend to wipe out the entire Yu Clan?

23
00:02:16,727 --> 00:02:18,180
I came to find Shuo Xuan.

24
00:02:18,180 --> 00:02:20,759
You aren't worthy of speaking her name.

25
00:02:22,808 --> 00:02:24,868
I do not want to harm you.

26
00:02:25,847 --> 00:02:29,087
You are not allowed to trespass the Sea of Clear Skies.

27
00:02:29,087 --> 00:02:30,747
Young Lord.

28
00:02:38,807 --> 00:02:40,928
Young Lord, please follow me.

29
00:02:55,367 --> 00:02:57,308
What is going on?

30
00:03:11,868 --> 00:03:14,388
Shuo Xuan, you...

31
00:03:15,008 --> 00:03:18,447
After Her Lordship's true form fell into a deep sleep,

32
00:03:18,447 --> 00:03:22,907
Shuo Xuan used Meditation Spell to replace Kun's consciousness

33
00:03:23,548 --> 00:03:25,928
and control her body.

34
00:03:25,928 --> 00:03:27,548
 Yue Qi, you have finally come. 

35
00:03:27,548 --> 00:03:28,868
 Yue Qi, you have finally come. 

36
00:03:28,868 --> 00:03:30,667
Why do you want Rehai?

37
00:03:30,667 --> 00:03:34,967
 Why? The reason lies above you. 

38
00:03:53,367 --> 00:03:59,628
Many of our people were injured in this battle and are recuperating here.

39
00:04:04,588 --> 00:04:07,208
I cannot make decisions regarding Rehai.

40
00:04:07,208 --> 00:04:09,768
But I will consult with Zhaoyan.

41
00:04:09,768 --> 00:04:11,827
You must not.

42
00:04:18,588 --> 00:04:21,467
 Ying Xuwei, what are you here for? 

43
00:04:21,467 --> 00:04:23,388
 This has nothing to do with you. 

44
00:04:23,388 --> 00:04:25,648
You shall not lay your hands on Rehai.

45
00:04:25,648 --> 00:04:29,068
 Then I will send Kun to the human world. 

46
00:04:29,068 --> 00:04:30,188
Don't.

47
00:04:30,188 --> 00:04:34,447
Shuo Xuan, let's just tell them...

48
00:04:35,307 --> 00:04:37,667
the real reason.

49
00:04:39,667 --> 00:04:41,887
Her Lordship's consciousness has fallen into slumber.

50
00:04:41,887 --> 00:04:47,088
Kun's body instinctively needs energy to heal the wounds from the battle.

51
00:04:49,427 --> 00:04:54,848
Repressing this instinct alone has already exhausted Shuo Xuan.

52
00:04:56,307 --> 00:04:58,488
Without the power of Rehai,

53
00:04:58,488 --> 00:05:01,408
eventually, she won't be able to hold on.

54
00:05:01,408 --> 00:05:06,467
So you want the power of Rehai to cure Zhu Yu.

55
00:05:08,327 --> 00:05:11,327
Rehai can only provide temporary relief.

56
00:05:11,327 --> 00:05:15,888
If Kun cannot complete the transformation,

57
00:05:15,888 --> 00:05:22,388
your Yu Clan, including Zhu Yu, must enter the time stasis.

58
00:05:22,388 --> 00:05:23,687
 Ying Xuwei, 

59
00:05:23,687 --> 00:05:26,648
 do you want to see a catastrophe in the human world again? 

60
00:05:30,268 --> 00:05:32,447
I have an idea.

61
00:05:32,447 --> 00:05:34,667
Let's hear it.

62
00:05:34,667 --> 00:05:36,728
I possess the bloodline of Kun.

63
00:05:36,728 --> 00:05:41,940
I can provide my spiritual power to Zhu Yu to calm her instincts.

64
00:05:41,940 --> 00:05:45,807
In this way, it will not affect the human world.

65
00:05:45,807 --> 00:05:48,048
Have you thought it through?

66
00:05:48,907 --> 00:05:50,968
Zhu Yu has been sleeping for ten thousand years.

67
00:05:50,968 --> 00:05:56,127
Providing her with your spiritual power could be fatal to you.

68
00:05:56,127 --> 00:05:58,388
 At least you still have a conscience. 

69
00:06:00,207 --> 00:06:01,887
But I have a condition.

70
00:06:01,887 --> 00:06:06,307
The sleeping Yu Clan will enter the time stasis together with Zhu Yu.

71
00:06:06,307 --> 00:06:09,767
The awakened Yu Clan may return to the sea.

72
00:06:09,767 --> 00:06:13,027
 - Yue Qi, how dare you?  
 - Shuo Xuan.

73
00:06:13,027 --> 00:06:18,220
To seize Rehai to treat the Yu Clan, we harmed innocent humans.

74
00:06:18,220 --> 00:06:20,959
We cannot make the same mistake again.

75
00:06:23,933 --> 00:06:25,794
Even if we lose,

76
00:06:27,107 --> 00:06:29,087
our Yu Clan...

77
00:06:31,400 --> 00:06:33,620
mustn't lose our dignity.

78
00:06:40,227 --> 00:06:41,907
Young Lord.

79
00:06:46,307 --> 00:06:48,148
Young Lord.

80
00:06:53,628 --> 00:06:55,808
I'm counting on you.

81
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:02,940
I'm also responsible for the Yu Clan.

82
00:07:08,388 --> 00:07:09,907
Shuo Xuan,

83
00:07:10,948 --> 00:07:13,760
I didn't fulfill my duty as the daughter.

84
00:07:13,760 --> 00:07:16,300
After this is settled,

85
00:07:16,300 --> 00:07:18,767
you should take over as the Young Lord.

86
00:07:18,767 --> 00:07:22,588
 Yue Qi, what do you mean? Apologizing to the Yu Clan? 

87
00:07:22,588 --> 00:07:25,268
 Or did you realize they're your burden now? 

88
00:07:25,268 --> 00:07:27,028
Shuo Xuan!

89
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:30,821
I am Zhu Yu's daughter,

90
00:07:30,821 --> 00:07:33,960
but I've never lived among the Yu Clan.

91
00:07:33,960 --> 00:07:37,781
Shuo Xuan understands and cares for them more than I do.

92
00:07:37,781 --> 00:07:39,840
She is more suitable for the role.

93
00:07:42,907 --> 00:07:46,268
Commander Ying, what do you think of it?

94
00:07:53,547 --> 00:07:55,407
I agree.

95
00:07:58,667 --> 00:08:03,527
Then, we must trouble you to open the Mist Soul afterward.

96
00:08:40,520 --> 00:08:42,700
Young Lord!

97
00:08:44,108 --> 00:08:45,967
Thank you.

98
00:08:53,667 --> 00:08:55,427
Ying Xuwei.

99
00:09:23,388 --> 00:09:26,807
I will follow Her Lordship into the time stasis.

100
00:09:28,787 --> 00:09:30,407
Shuo Xuan.

101
00:09:34,147 --> 00:09:36,167
Entering the time stasis...

102
00:09:37,348 --> 00:09:39,467
equals eternal imprisonment.

103
00:09:42,507 --> 00:09:44,347
You are young.

104
00:09:49,188 --> 00:09:51,567
If we migrate to the sea,

105
00:09:51,567 --> 00:09:53,807
we can start over again.

106
00:09:56,387 --> 00:09:58,728
Her Lordship is our savior.

107
00:09:58,728 --> 00:10:01,167
I should stay by her side.

108
00:10:02,047 --> 00:10:06,527
I'm also doing you a favor by accompanying Her Lordship.

109
00:10:06,527 --> 00:10:08,728
From now on, we are even.

110
00:10:12,848 --> 00:10:17,540
I am willing to follow Her Lordship to the time stasis.

111
00:10:18,128 --> 00:10:23,627
 I am willing to follow Her Lordship to the time stasis. 

112
00:10:23,627 --> 00:10:25,128
You...

113
00:10:33,420 --> 00:10:35,008
I knew it.

114
00:10:35,008 --> 00:10:38,928
We Yu Clan are all fearless warriors.

115
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:50,700
Shuo Xuan.

116
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:55,221
Please take care of her.

117
00:10:56,907 --> 00:10:59,027
She is also my mother.

118
00:11:47,428 --> 00:11:49,047
Mother.

119
00:12:12,948 --> 00:12:14,427
Xiaoyuan,

120
00:12:15,188 --> 00:12:17,407
go back to rest.

121
00:13:12,308 --> 00:13:16,808
Now, everything

122
00:13:16,808 --> 00:13:19,368
is finally over.

123
00:13:22,027 --> 00:13:24,928
At the grand ceremony, the drums will sound.

124
00:13:25,987 --> 00:13:28,807
The flower will pass on. The dancer will be found.

125
00:13:28,807 --> 00:13:31,967
Beautiful women will sing harmonious songs.

126
00:13:33,627 --> 00:13:36,828
Spring orchids and autumn chrysanthemums

127
00:13:36,828 --> 00:13:39,587
shall never cease...

128
00:13:41,208 --> 00:13:43,208
through the ages.

129
00:14:35,108 --> 00:14:40,067
Second Sister, your left hand is about to rust.

130
00:14:57,720 --> 00:14:59,348
Second Sister.

131
00:14:59,348 --> 00:15:04,628
If you don't wake up, mushrooms will grow on you.

132
00:15:08,188 --> 00:15:12,100
Second Sister, do you want to go and bask in the sun?

133
00:15:12,100 --> 00:15:15,108
I'll take you out in a moment.

134
00:15:38,587 --> 00:15:41,707
It's finally over.

135
00:15:42,640 --> 00:15:44,228
Yes.

136
00:15:44,228 --> 00:15:46,707
The Yu Clan has entered the time stasis.

137
00:15:46,707 --> 00:15:48,888
And there are no disasters in the human world.

138
00:15:48,888 --> 00:15:51,708
This is the best possible ending.

139
00:15:57,547 --> 00:16:01,648
You have been greatly weakened. You must rest well.

140
00:16:06,868 --> 00:16:09,207
We've arrived at the western wasteland.

141
00:16:17,067 --> 00:16:19,128
Do you remember, Young Xiu?

142
00:16:20,108 --> 00:16:24,587
This is where we met Zhaoyan and Young Yue.

143
00:16:26,787 --> 00:16:30,888
Back then, they were all with us.

144
00:16:42,640 --> 00:16:45,960
Everyone, thank you.

145
00:16:47,120 --> 00:16:49,260
Let's part ways from here.

146
00:16:53,388 --> 00:16:56,408
Miss Yue, where are you going?

147
00:17:01,228 --> 00:17:03,887
Will you do something foolish?

148
00:17:05,047 --> 00:17:06,928
Of course not.

149
00:17:13,268 --> 00:17:16,908
People meet and part like duckweed. Don't force it.

150
00:17:18,867 --> 00:17:22,468
Young Yue, take care.

151
00:17:23,600 --> 00:17:25,239
Xian Qing.

152
00:17:26,120 --> 00:17:27,719
Zhaoyan.

153
00:17:29,708 --> 00:17:31,407
Sister Ming Xiu.

154
00:17:34,428 --> 00:17:37,047
You take care as well.

155
00:17:37,047 --> 00:17:38,748
You too.

156
00:18:34,287 --> 00:18:36,008
And you?

157
00:18:39,988 --> 00:18:41,647
I...

158
00:18:45,207 --> 00:18:47,627
I want to seek the art of eternal life.

159
00:18:51,147 --> 00:18:53,527
Maiming borrowed my life before.

160
00:18:53,527 --> 00:18:56,067
Although the curse has been lifted,

161
00:18:56,067 --> 00:19:00,088
the lifespan he took from me has not been returned.

162
00:19:00,088 --> 00:19:03,708
The time I have left is not much.

163
00:19:05,028 --> 00:19:06,687
If I were to die like this,

164
00:19:06,687 --> 00:19:09,508
even if fate allows us to meet again,

165
00:19:10,908 --> 00:19:15,188
I certainly would not remember the time I had with you.

166
00:19:17,400 --> 00:19:19,660
I will not accept that.

167
00:19:21,988 --> 00:19:24,027
I will go with you.

168
00:19:38,387 --> 00:19:40,167
And you, Young Xiu?

169
00:19:41,128 --> 00:19:46,007
I'll return to Mount Yuqing. You can have the Yunlai Stone.

170
00:19:51,708 --> 00:19:55,588
Young Xiu, take care of yourself.

171
00:19:56,428 --> 00:19:58,808
You should take care of yourself as well.

172
00:19:58,808 --> 00:20:00,608
Miss Ming, take care.

173
00:20:01,347 --> 00:20:03,027
Goodbye.

174
00:20:19,228 --> 00:20:21,868
If we miss Miss Ming,

175
00:20:21,868 --> 00:20:24,428
we can go see her at Mount Yuqing.

176
00:20:25,347 --> 00:20:27,447
But Miss Yue...

177
00:20:31,888 --> 00:20:34,367
We'll meet again if fate allows.

178
00:20:37,328 --> 00:20:40,400
We have witnessed how much Miss Yue has grown.

179
00:20:40,400 --> 00:20:44,300
I believe she will follow her heart.

