00:21:28,263 --> 00:21:32,615
♫  Piercing deep into my heart, it tears at me  ♫

183
00:21:32,615 --> 00:21:38,120
♫  Instead why not take my doomed fate away  ♫

184
00:21:38,120 --> 00:21:43,910
♫  The mirror reflects the shadows but remains invisible  ♫

185
00:21:43,910 --> 00:21:50,599
♫  Like those hidden emotions, icy and piercing  ♫

186
00:21:50,599 --> 00:21:52,755
♫  Using the lightest words  ♫

187
00:21:52,755 --> 00:21:54,983
♫  To make the harshest decisions  ♫

188
00:21:54,983 --> 00:22:02,727
♫  No different from a death sentence  ♫

189
00:22:04,175 --> 00:22:09,877
♫  If you truly can bear to leave with the wind  ♫

190
00:22:09,877 --> 00:22:15,500
♫  How come tears suddenly shimmer in your eyes?  ♫

191
00:22:15,500 --> 00:22:17,039
Master,

192
00:22:18,183 --> 00:22:19,883
I'm back.

193
00:22:21,070 --> 00:22:25,020
♫  Even the embraces feel forced  ♫

194
00:22:25,020 --> 00:22:27,580
During this time,

195
00:22:27,580 --> 00:22:29,830
I've experienced a lot.

196
00:22:30,823 --> 00:22:33,083
And I finally understood

197
00:22:33,083 --> 00:22:38,011
why you had given up your life for the lives of others.

198
00:22:38,011 --> 00:22:44,744
♫  If our next meeting is uncertain, don't eavesdrop on me in my dreams  ♫

199
00:22:44,744 --> 00:22:48,504
Now, I think...

200
00:22:50,024 --> 00:22:52,444
I've made the same decision as you.

201
00:22:55,263 --> 00:22:57,164
Right.

202
00:22:57,164 --> 00:22:59,044
As for Xian Qing.

203
00:22:59,044 --> 00:23:02,944
This thousand-year-old wolf demon had no desires before.

204
00:23:02,944 --> 00:23:06,624
But now, he also has someone he cares for.

205
00:23:06,624 --> 00:23:09,144
That he could end up with Zhaoyan,

206
00:23:10,063 --> 00:23:16,203
I think, is also a gift granted to him by the endless time.

207
00:23:30,324 --> 00:23:31,843
Master,

208
00:23:33,184 --> 00:23:37,263
your Xiu'er has grown up.

209
00:23:37,263 --> 00:23:43,023
♫  If you truly can bear to leave with the wind  ♫

210
00:23:43,023 --> 00:23:48,718
♫  How come tears suddenly shimmer in your eyes?  ♫

211
00:23:48,718 --> 00:23:53,959
♫  What was thought to be evergreen withers between my fingers  ♫

212
00:23:53,959 --> 00:23:59,854
♫  Even the embraces feel forced  ♫

213
00:23:59,854 --> 00:24:05,551
♫  If the flowing water and fallen flowers are all fate  ♫

214
00:24:05,551 --> 00:24:10,804
♫  Don't talk about who failed love  ♫

