00:24:13,583 --> 00:24:17,681
♫  If our next meeting is uncertain, don't eavesdrop on me in my dreams  ♫

217
00:24:17,681 --> 00:24:23,023
♫  Humming that tune of lovesickness  ♫

218
00:24:24,971 --> 00:24:30,404
♫  In the dream  ♫

219
00:24:31,695 --> 00:24:36,712
♫  humming that tune of lovesickness  ♫

220
00:24:39,984 --> 00:24:42,463
I'm an old person.

221
00:24:42,463 --> 00:24:44,923
I will need you to take care of me.

222
00:24:46,403 --> 00:24:48,003
Okay.

223
00:24:48,743 --> 00:24:50,583
How is your health?

224
00:24:50,583 --> 00:24:51,984
Fine.

225
00:24:51,984 --> 00:24:55,163
I quite enjoy having you take care of me.

226
00:24:57,683 --> 00:25:00,923
We should be near the place in the legend now.

227
00:25:20,303 --> 00:25:23,443
This art of eternity truly left no trace.

228
00:25:23,443 --> 00:25:26,944
We've been searching for days, but without success.

229
00:25:26,944 --> 00:25:29,683
I'm afraid we've started this journey in vain.

230
00:25:31,263 --> 00:25:35,344
The world is vast. We will find it eventually.

231
00:25:37,218 --> 00:25:39,384
But I don't want it anymore.

232
00:25:43,964 --> 00:25:46,463
Since it cannot be found,

233
00:25:46,463 --> 00:25:50,183
I will cultivate alongside you to seek immortality.

234
00:25:50,183 --> 00:25:52,044
How about it?

235
00:25:52,044 --> 00:25:54,123
Are you sure about this?

236
00:25:59,244 --> 00:26:02,123
Although this place is secluded,

237
00:26:02,123 --> 00:26:04,263
there are countless creatures here.

238
00:26:04,263 --> 00:26:08,323
These plants also seem especially lush.

239
00:26:08,323 --> 00:26:10,603
Is this the nimbus you spoke of?

240
00:26:12,363 --> 00:26:14,724
This is indeed a good place for recuperating.

241
00:26:14,724 --> 00:26:17,964
Good. Then let's cultivate here.

242
00:26:20,843 --> 00:26:24,484
But I have no strength left now.

243
00:26:25,123 --> 00:26:28,064
I'm afraid I'll need you to help me up.

244
00:26:34,043 --> 00:26:36,663
You've lost all your strength.

245
00:26:37,484 --> 00:26:41,684
I guess you can't help me with my hairpin anymore.

246
00:26:44,123 --> 00:26:45,863
Of course I can.

247
00:26:47,083 --> 00:26:51,624
But do you really understand the loyalty of the Wolf Tribe?

248
00:26:51,624 --> 00:26:56,844
We've been through so much. It's about time, isn't it?

249
00:28:26,843 --> 00:28:30,503
I am already aware of your intentions from the stream of memories.

250
00:28:30,503 --> 00:28:33,043
You wish to exchange the life of Yue Jinzhao?

251
00:28:33,043 --> 00:28:34,523
Yes.

252
00:28:35,323 --> 00:28:37,484
I want Jinzhao to come back.

253
00:28:37,484 --> 00:28:41,523
If you have a wish, you must make a sacrifice.

254
00:28:41,523 --> 00:28:43,603
You can only exchange for his life

255
00:28:43,603 --> 00:28:47,784
at the cost of your existence.

256
00:28:48,404 --> 00:28:49,884
Okay.

257
00:28:50,484 --> 00:28:55,164
The so-called existence refers to all your memories

258
00:28:55,164 --> 00:28:58,803
and the memories others have of you.

259
00:28:58,803 --> 00:29:00,603
When your existence disappears,

